org.apache.taverna.workflowmodel.processor.iteration

Class AbstractIterationStrategyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • org.apache.taverna.workflowmodel.processor.iteration.AbstractIterationStrategyNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, MutableTreeNode, TreeNode, IterationStrategyNode, WorkflowItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompletionHandlingAbstractIterationStrategyNode, NamedInputPortNode, TerminalNode

    public abstract class AbstractIterationStrategyNode
extends DefaultMutableTreeNode
implements IterationStrategyNode
    Abstract superclass for implementations of IterationStrategyNode, adds logic to connect nodes together and convenience methods to push jobs and completion events up to the parent node.
    Author:
    Tom Oinn, Stian Soiland-Reyes
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
